{"word":"G3701 - ὀπτασία - optasía - op-tas-ee'-ah - Vision","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀπτασία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>optasía"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>op-tas-ee'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Vision"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"தரிசனம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. the act of exhibiting oneself to view"},{"paragraph":"2. a sight, a vision"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G3700 - ὀπτάνομαι - optánomai - op-tan'-om-ahee/3700\">G3700</a>; <i>visuality</i>, that is, (concretely) an <i>apparition:</i> - vision."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2029 - ἐποπτεύω - epopteúō - ep-opt-yoo'-o/2029\">G2029</a>, <a href=\"#/G2030 - ἐπόπτης - epóptēs - ep-op'-tace/2030\">G2030</a>, <a href=\"#/G3700 - ὀπτάνομαι - optánomai - op-tan'-om-ahee/3700\">G3700</a>, <a href=\"#/G3701 - ὀπτασία - optasía - op-tas-ee'-ah/3701\">G3701</a>, <a href=\"#/G845 - αὐτόπτης - autóptēs - ow-top'-tace/845\">G845</a>, <a href=\"#/G991 - βλέπω - blépō - blep'-o/991\">G991</a>"}]}